OL,3,COlivia Pratt-Korbel's family 'back at
OL,4,Csquare one' over 'Face the Family' bill
OL,6,FOlivia's mum told ITV News reporter
OL,7,FChloe Keedy they are "still fighting"
OL,8,Ffor a change in the law to force
OL,9,Foffenders into attending sentencing
OL,10,Fhearings
OL,12,FWhen Cheryl Korbel found out that the
OL,13,FLabour conference would be held in her
OL,14,Fhome city of Liverpool, she knew she
OL,15,Fneeded to be there.
OL,17,FIt's just over a year since she met
OL,18,Fthe then Prime Minister, Rishi Sunak,
OL,19,Fas he promised to pass a bill that
OL,20,Fwould force killers to attend court on
OL,21,Fthe day of their sentencing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
