OL,3,COlivia Pratt-Korbel's family 'back at
OL,4,Csquare one' over 'Face the Family' bill
OL,6,FThat promise meant everything to
OL,7,FCheryl.
OL,9,FHer daughter, nine-year-old Olivia
OL,10,FPratt-Korbel, was shot dead in their
OL,11,Ffamily home on August 22, 2022.
OL,13,FLast year, following a trial at
OL,14,FManchester Crown Court, Thomas Cashman
OL,15,Fwas convicted of her murder.
OL,17,FBut on the day of his sentencing he
OL,18,Frefused to appear in the dock, to
OL,19,Flisten to the judge or hear the impact
OL,20,Fstatements that her mum and sister
OL,21,FChloe had written.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
