OL,3,COlivia Pratt-Korbel's family 'back at
OL,4,Csquare one' over 'Face the Family' bill
OL,6,FSince then, the family has been
OL,7,Fcampaigning to get the law changed so
OL,8,Fthat criminals are forced to face
OL,9,Ftheir victim's families in court.
OL,11,FLast summer I went with them to
OL,12,FDowning Street - where the prime
OL,13,Fminister promised he would pass
OL,14,FOlivia's law before the next election.
OL,15,FThe same day, Sir Keir Starmer - then
OL,16,Fleader of the opposition - told them
OL,17,Fthe bill had his full support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
