OL,3,COlivia Pratt-Korbel's family 'back at
OL,4,Csquare one' over 'Face the Family' bill
OL,6,FMore than a year on - the election has
OL,7,Fpassed, but the bill hasn't. And in a
OL,8,Fmeeting with the Home Secretary,
OL,9,FYvette Cooper, Olivia's mum and aunt
OL,10,FAntonia told her they feel as though
OL,11,Fthey are back at square one.
OL,13,F"We were forced to go to the trial for
OL,14,Ffour weeks," said Cheryl. "Why can't
OL,15,Fthey be forced to be there at the end?"
OL,17,FMs Cooper told Cheryl and Olivia's
OL,18,Faunt Antonia that she felt "fury and
OL,19,Fanger that perpetrators can get away
OL,20,Fwith this".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
