OL,3,COlivia Pratt-Korbel's family 'back at
OL,4,Csquare one' over 'Face the Family' bill
OL,6,FShe said: "It's a total disgrace. To
OL,7,Fbe in your situation and then not even
OL,8,Fhaving someone face justice - It's an
OL,9,Fabsolute disgrace and the law needs to
OL,10,Fbe changed."
OL,12,FBut they have heard that one before.
OL,14,FI asked the home Secretary if she
OL,15,Fcould guarantee that we wouldn't still
OL,16,Fbe having this conversation in another
OL,17,Fyear's time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
