OL,3,COlivia Pratt-Korbel's family 'back at
OL,4,Csquare one' over 'Face the Family' bill
OL,6,F"We can't be," she told me. "We have
OL,7,Fto get this through as quickly as
OL,8,Fpossible. I just think the family
OL,9,Fcannot wait any longer.
OL,11,F"Other families cannot go through this
OL,12,Fdeep injustice. Perpetrators have to
OL,13,Fface court, they have to face
OL,14,Ffamilies."
OL,16,FOlivia's mum has told me many times
OL,17,Fthat she can no longer trust any
OL,18,Fpoliticians, because they've been let
OL,19,Fdown. She told me that today had made
OL,20,Fher feel "hopeful", but that "trust
OL,21,Fhas got to be built".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
