OL,3,COlivia Pratt-Korbel's family 'back at
OL,4,Csquare one' over 'Face the Family' bill
OL,6,FGetting the bill passed quickly is one
OL,7,Fof their top priorities. Another, they
OL,8,Ftell me, is ensuring that it applies
OL,9,Fto all offenders, and not just those
OL,10,Fthe prime minister has referred to as
OL,11,F"serious offenders".
OL,13,FTwo years since Olivia's death, they
OL,14,Ftell me it is her that gives them the
OL,15,Fstrength to keep fighting on behalf of
OL,16,Fother families.
OL,18,F"Olivia doesn't have a voice, so we're
OL,19,Fher voice now," said Cheryl.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
