OL,3,COlivia Pratt-Korbel's family 'back at
OL,4,Csquare one' over 'Face the Family' bill
OL,6,F"She was only 9 but she had a little
OL,7,Ffire in her belly. That gives us the
OL,8,Ffire in our belly to keep fighting."
OL,10,FWhat they still don't know, is how
OL,11,Fmuch longer they will have to keep
OL,12,Ffighting for.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
